did.head: Overview
did.unittitle: Stanford University, Department of English, honors theses
did.abstract: Honors theses written by undergraduate students in the Stanford University Department of English.

repository.label: Repository:
repository.corpname: Dept. of Special Collections & University Archives.

acqinfo.p: This collection was transferred to the Stanford University Archives by the Department of English in 1989 and 1993, and from the Hume Writing Center in 2011.

accessrestrict.head: Information about Access
accessrestrict.p: The collection is open for research; material must be requested at least 48 hours in advance of intended use. No photocopies may be made.

userestrict.head: Ownership & Copyright
userestrict.p: Copyright is retained by the creators for materials they have authored or otherwise produced. Transmission or reproduction of materials requires the written permission of the copyright owner.

prefercite.head: Cite As
prefercite.p: [identification of item], Stanford University, Department of English, Honors Theses (SC4-3891). Dept. of Special Collections and University Archives, Stanford University Libraries, Stanford, Calif.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: This collection consists of honors theses written by undergraduate students in the Stanford University Department of English.
